Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很久没有到過這種偏僻的鄉下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎都認不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,叮咚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊
