Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早安  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,梓 也太大膽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,實在 讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,止不住興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是使 人神魂 顛倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂~ 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我 什麼時候說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有當然如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,復合是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有那種事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也只是想做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那我掛電話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,前男友一直纏著  要復合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,前男友一直纏著  要復合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上是充電線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前  就是一個怪咖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 才不是那種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是那種坦率的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我姐啊 以前就很會讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是資優生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,美月~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我姐以前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才被吸引後結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,學生時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就一直交往了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在鄉下也~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有別的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以   現在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自然而然  就是結婚嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  這樣子噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  我爸媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,總是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一直只誇我姐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我總是被她拿去比較
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一直很嫉妒我姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  家裡有WaiFai器用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很少  用網絡功能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎   知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫你 早點休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
