Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.16,1:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.42,1:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要給我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.52,1:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,給我 給我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.08,1:01:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.08,1:01:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.08,1:01:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.08,1:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.08,1:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快點給我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.28,1:01:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.28,1:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,使徑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.28,1:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.28,1:01:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,已經到了極點了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.30,1:01:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.30,1:01:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
