Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.14,1:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.14,1:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.14,1:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.14,1:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也覺得很爽
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.46,1:03:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.46,1:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣內射不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.68,1:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係  這樣比較爽
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.58,1:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.58,1:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,難不成是第一次內射
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.60,1:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你爽就沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.50,1:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然爽啦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.36,1:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我在梓的引誘下我們做愛了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.80,1:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小姨子使我神魂顛倒
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.66,1:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不能允許的關係
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.92,1:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還是使我無法抗拒
