Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.54,1:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.54,1:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.08,1:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明天還能工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.56,1:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.56,1:04:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明天  看情況     休息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.56,1:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,應該休息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.66,1:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天看看醫生吧
